///////////////////////////////////////
Naming rule: 
	There is a principle that the more wider scope , the more simpler name

Scope: File / Class / Function


Module(File) Name: modulename
Class Name: ClassName
Argument Name : argument_name
Function Name ： functionName
Private Function Name ： _functionName

Var of File : VARIABLE_NAME
Var of Class :	_VariableName
Var of function : _Variable_Name


Section name of ini file : Config_File_Name
Key name of ini file : key_name_of_ini_file 
